Net-LDAP-ADGroup version 0.02
=============================

A basic extension of Net::LDAP, provides methods: ismembers and allgroups.
These methods can be used to easily check group membership in an
applications

There is an example script using the module in the example folder of this
distribution.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Net::LDAP

